sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as News List Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open news list
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query published news (paged, desc by date)
    DB-->>LW: Paginated published articles
    LW-->>UI: Render list and filter drawer

    User->>UI: Search/filter/paginate
    UI->>LW: Update URL-bound/filter properties
    LW->>DB: Re-query with conditions
    DB-->>LW: Updated paginated result
    LW-->>UI: Re-render article list

    User->>UI: Open one article
    UI->>LW: Navigate to article slug route
    LW-->>UI: Load article view page
